  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nWhen I try to deploy to Optimistic Kovan via Truffle dashboards, I cannot edit the gas limit.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Add Optimistic Kovan to Metamask wallet and truffle config\r\n2. `truffle migrate --network dashboards`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nShould be able to sign and deploy\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n<img width=\"363\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-05-17 at 2 59 28 PM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17280653/168917058-bc8f5352-237e-487f-b900-9f66b15fede0.png\">\r\n\r\ngasLimit is not being properly specified\r\n`TypeError: Cannot read properties of null (reading 'gasLimit')`\r\n\r\nI think the problem is probably deeper with Optimism Kovan being finnicky, but the EDIT button isn't there regardless.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MacOS\r\n* Ethereum client: 0.8.13\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): v5.5.12\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v16.14.2\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.14.16\r\n",
